        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tomshi/" class="name">tomshi</a>

            <span class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>

        <span content="2008-09-07" class="main-meta">2008-09-07 10:02:54</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/1490826/">对谁狠，都不如对自己人更狠</a></h2>

